entries.femaleVariant: Hop in.
Sure.
[Get out] We'll meet there.
Let's get going.
On our way.
We'll meet on site. Need to get a few things together first.
OK… Just not too long, all right?
Lemme get everything prepped. You make sure the wreath's snug on you.
[Put on headset] Ready.
Ready when you are.
No time to lose. We gotta go there.
I let her go back to Clouds. Coulda stopped her but I didn't...
Think I'll try calling Wakako. Fixer Fingers mentioned.
Thought of an angle to run on her?
Why would I need one?
Know where we can get our hands on an XBD. Might not be a Death's Head, but it'll be a start.
Saw a smut shop on Jig-Jig Street. All kinds of stuff there.
Saw a virtu pusher on Jig-Jig Street. Had a wide selection.
Was on a contract taken out on a guy named Jotaro Shobo.
Think you might find a Death's Head?
Could have what we're looking for.
Even if she knows the studio's location, she's not gonna spill. Be putting her neck on the line.
Want to you describe what you see. Might catch something I'd miss.
You'll watch while I edit in real-time. The ol' one-two.
Hm. M'kay. I'm buyin' the braindance. We can analyze, play detective.
Need to find out where they scroll these things.
Mhm. The Mox put a bounty on his head. So you were the one to cut him down?
Found out he was dealin' in XBDs, sourced from someone on Jig-Jig Street. Got the coordinates.
Can't hurt to try.
Definitely. Ride with me?
Death's Head – heard the term used, ever?
Death's Head symbol bring anything to mind? Anything, doesn't matter how small.
This industry... I mean, market's lookin' for every kind of fetish out there. It's cavernous. But an XBD outfit'd be on the move almost always.
Makes 'em harder to nab, harder to sting.
Can't afford to lose our nerve.
Don't worry, we'll find her.
Don't worry, we'll find her. I know it.
Losing our cool won't do us any favors. It's a waste of time.
Only lead we got's an XBD. Where's that get us?
We'll fuckin' find what's left of her butchered corpse.
And you two... got along swimmingly, didn't ya? Exchange numbers, too?
How I got the info shouldn't matter.
Fingers isn't that bad.
Can we not lose our cool? Said what I needed to learn what we now know.
Trust me, Judy – compared to the pieces of shit I scrape off my shoe every day…
Two birds of a fucking feather.
We also know we're lookin' for something related to the Death's Head. Better than nothing.
Oh, I'm cool. Real fuckin' cool with the fact Ev's probably already dead!
You don't know that. And I'm sure as hell not gonna squander precious minutes we could spend lookin'.
Dark net domain, that's our best bet. Let's stick to the plan.
Fine. Here's hoping you turn up something useful.
Meantime, see if I can't find something on the NCP domain.
Hm, took your sweet time getting to Fingers...
Drop it, will ya?
All right, the pusher – what about him?
I'll wait in the van.
Really? Ya seemed forgiving to me, like you were letting him off easy.
Fingers doesn't come close to being half their brand of rotten.
Got no fucking words, V, none…
Hey! Keep it together! Wanna give up, now?
No...
Need to figure out where they're scrollin' this stuff. Gotta be a rat-hole of some sort, doubt they do much shooting on location.
Yeah, gotta be somewhere quiet, out of the way.
Could be we'd see something to point us in their direction in one of their virtus.
Have to be real gonks to leave a clue…
Lemme think for a sec.
I'll take a look around Jig-Jig Street.
Know a fixer in Westbrook. I'll drop her a line.
V, fixers don't hand out information right and left.
Done a couple of things for her, not that she owes me… But let's see what she has to say.
I don't get your optimism. Still sounds like a big fat nothing to me.
Got a better idea?
Everyone, everything leaves a trace behind.
Got a better idea?
Matter of fact, I do. A domain called "Pleasures of Night City" – there's a twin of it on the dark net.
Everyone, everything leaves something behind. Just need to know where to look.
Lucky for me, I'm runnin' around with the best BD specialist in town. That's an extra pair of expert eyes.
Well, your BD expert has a better idea. "Pleasures of Night City," a domain with its twin on the dark net.
Let's give the dark net site a shot.
Think I've got a better idea.
Fine.
It's not her.
Would've been downright strange if the recording we found was hers…
That supposed to make me feel better?
Of course. Of all the freaks in Night City, it had to be fuckin' scavs?
Building must've been abandoned for a while if they've annexed it.
Every kind of thing goes on there. Might stumble on something useful.
I know a local fixer.
[Get in]
